OL,5,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,6,     FA man faces life-changing injuries
OL,7,     Fafter a firework explodes in his
OL,8,     Fhand, and a patient is treated for
OL,9,     Fsevere facial burns following an
OL,10,     Faccident with a gas canister at
OL,11,     Fhis workplace.
OL,12,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FOn another busy night in one of
OL,14,     Fthe UK's major trauma centres, a
OL,15,     Fpatient ignores hospital policy
OL,16,     Fand refuses to leave, while Dr
OL,17,     FAustin looks after a patient who
OL,18,     Fhas broken her ankle.
