OL,5,G2300 Trauma Room One
OL,6,     FA man arrives in theatre with
OL,7,     Fagonising back pain and doctors
OL,8,     Fsuspect a cancerous tumour is
OL,9,     Fcompressing his spinal cord. He
OL,10,     Fneeds an urgent operation using a
OL,11,     Fhi-tech robot to remove it. (Ep3)
OL,12,G0000 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Natalia Spierings struggles to
OL,14,     Fsee acne hidden with makeup by a
OL,15,     Fpatient. Dr Toby Nelson is shocked
OL,16,     Fby a patient's DIY attempt on a
OL,17,     Fcyst. Dr Adil Sheraz tackles a
OL,18,     Fstubborn lipoma.
