OL,5,G0100 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FA landlord calls in help when some
OL,7,     Fclued-up squatters take over a
OL,8,     Fdisused pub, and a widow faces
OL,9,     Ftrouble when she tries to evict a
OL,10,     Ffamily who owe her thousands in
OL,11,     Frent.
OL,12,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FYorkshire's A&E struggles with too
OL,14,     Fmany patients and not enough room
OL,15,     Ffor them as they work to treat
OL,16,     Finternal chest wounds, a collapsed
OL,17,     Flung and a back injury.
